    <div class="-mx-10 mt-10 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <Image src={gab} alt="Gabriel Zambrano photo" class="inline-block lg:rounded-sm"/>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-10 text-balance leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        I am a skilled web developer, who combines technical and business expertise with a passion for creating visually appealing and user-friendly websites.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-10 space-y-5 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
